          "anchor": "Discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Use this property to specify the type of experience to display when someone engages writing tools for a text input view. The system does its best to provide the requested UI, but might offer a more limited experience if required capabilities arenâ€™t available. The default value of this property is ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.uikit/documentation/UIKit/UIWritingToolsBehavior/default",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ", which lets the system choose the most appropriate experience for the current device.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Set the value of this property to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.uikit/documentation/UIKit/UIWritingToolsBehavior/none",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " if you want to prevent someone from using the writing tools with your view.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
